data.description: Beautifully updated move in ready split plan home looking for new owners to move in and enjoy. Posh upgrades and terrific location! Home greets with high ceilings, freshly painted interior and exterior plus all newly installed luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout. Home offers open floor plan with newly installed granite island and all new designer picked paint, lighting and fans. Kitchen and baths have all been updated. Family room off-the kitchen overlooks huge covered patio and fully fenced backyard with rear neighbors separated by a large canal. Enjoy preparing your meals in the modern updated well lit kitchen with lots of cabinets and stainless appliances. So great having an updated worry free home with a newer roof, brand new A/C, and newer hot water heater. Must see! Master bedroom has a big wall closet and wide window with views of back covered patio and private backyard.  The fully updated master bathroom has a new tub, shower, vanity, faucet and modern lights. Second bedroom has new remote controlled ceiling fans & great window for natural lighting. Third bedroom is garage conversion with huge closet and new designer picked remote controlled ceiling fan and lights. Inside utility room and bathroom just outside the third bedroom all including the newly installed LVP flooring. Enjoy your morning coffee on the updated covered back porch any season of the year that can easily be screened or enclosed. The large fenced back yard has a shed for storage, lots of space for toys like boats and RV parking plus front has an additional parking pad for off street parking. Private lot in a neighborhood with newer homes being built all around. Must see. Call today!
